# Ansible & Docker

- Keep the **flat Ansible layout** at repo root (`inventory/`, `playbooks/`, `roles/`)—do not nest under `ansible/` (PLAN §7.1).
- Machine secrets belong in **ansible-vault**-encrypted `inventory/group_vars/sparky.yml`; commit only `sparky.yml.example` (PLAN §10).
- Compose files must reference secrets via `env_file` or Docker secrets—not literal `environment:` secrets in tracked YAML (PLAN §10).
- Shell scripts under `scripts/` should pass **shellcheck**; suitable for CI per PLAN §22.
